vidheyan ( english : the servile ) is a 1993 indian malayalam film directed and written by adoor gopalakrishnan .   it is a cinematic adaptation of the novella bhaskara pattelarum ente jeevithavum by malayalam writer zacharia .   the film explores the master-slave dialectic in a south karnataka setting .   mammootty plays the lead role in the film , who received several accolades for his work .